00:00:09.210 --> 00:00:12.120
- [Narrator] We are the paradoxical ape.

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:14.453
Bipedal, naked, large brain,

00:00:17.348 --> 00:00:21.353
long the master of fire,
tools, and language,

00:00:21.353 --> 00:00:24.770
but still trying to understand ourselves.

00:00:25.672 --> 00:00:28.853
Aware that death is inevitable,

00:00:28.853 --> 00:00:30.936
yet filled with optimism.

00:00:32.281 --> 00:00:34.573
We grow up slowly.

00:00:34.573 --> 00:00:37.145
We hand down knowledge.

00:00:37.145 --> 00:00:39.228
We empathize and deceive.

00:00:40.690 --> 00:00:41.784
We shape the future

00:00:41.784 --> 00:00:46.075
from our shared understanding of the past.

00:00:46.075 --> 00:00:49.703
Carta brings together experts
from diverse disciplines

00:00:49.703 --> 00:00:52.902
to exchange insights on who we are

00:00:52.902 --> 00:00:54.569
and how we got here.

00:00:55.993 --> 00:00:57.623
An exploration made possible

00:00:57.623 --> 00:01:01.081
by the generosity of humans like you.

00:01:01.081 --> 00:01:03.664
(bouncy music)

00:01:15.144 --> 00:01:17.727
